Hkl Scan:

python hklscan.py controller/diffrace6c/e6cctrl <door_device_name>

UB Matrix:

python ubmatrixwidget.py controller/diffrace6c/e6cctrl

Hkl Alignment:

python diffractometeralignment.py controller/diffrace6c/e6cctrl <door_device_name>

<door_device_name> = p09/door/hastodt

If the door_device_name is supplied the connection is done automatically when the
 GUI is started.
